<p><b>Psychology of religion</b> is the <a href="/wiki/Psychology" title="Psychology">psychological</a> <a href="/wiki/Research" title="Research">study</a> of <a href="/wiki/Religious_experience" title="Religious experience">religious experiences</a>, <a href="/wiki/Belief" title="Belief">beliefs</a>, and activities.</p>
