<li><a href="http://www.robertaziz.com" class="external text" title="http://www.robertaziz.com" rel="nofollow">Website of leading Jungian scholar/ author, Dr. Robert Aziz</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.iacsr.com" class="external text" title="http://www.iacsr.com" rel="nofollow">International Association for the Scientific Study of Religion</a></li>
